article.description: Tuesday night's NIT game between UNC-Greensboro and Syracuse has been postponed and rescheduled for Wednesday night in the Carrier Dome due to a winter storm wreaking havoc in the Northeast.
article.headline: Winter storm postpones NIT game in Syracuse
article.linkText: Winter storm postpones NIT game in Syracuse
